Finite runner created with CSFML.

USAGE
 ./my_runner map.txt


OPTION
 -i                launch the game in infinity mode.
 -h                print the usage and quit.

USER INTERACTIONS
 W, Space_Key, or Up_Key    jump.
 R                          retry.
 S or Down_Key              stop the jump.
 Q or Left_Key              go to the left.
 D or Right_Key             go to the right.
 C                          return on the main menu.
 ESCAPE                     qui the game.
